<referable-content id="1c976e6510a14b5859b21a7e2016d423" xml:lang="en-US"><!--TextModulePath:/Informationen/New Jersey2/Ericsson Cloud Manager /Textblock Pool/IPv6--><title>External IdAM IPv6 Restriction</title>
   <rcbody>
      <note id="st4tb14315247883">
                           <p>When specifying an IPv6 endpoint for the <ph keyref="externalIdam"/>,
            use the Fully Qualified Domain Name (FQDN) and not just the IPv6 address, to identify
            the <ph keyref="externalIdam"/> endpoint.</p>
                        </note>
   </rcbody>
